title: THEY FILMED IT
description:
As the GOP prepare to take over the House and Nancy Pelosi departs from her position as Speaker, a new hagiography directed by her daughter has debuted on HBO. So, as Joe Biden fawns over her departure and the mainstream media once again participate in the whitewashing of politicians – how and where are we able to hold to account the most powerful and indeed richest members of congress? 
#nancypelosi #biden #hbomax
